&lt;h4 class=&#34;header-anchor-wrapper&#34;&gt;Analyze miss.
  &lt;a href=&#34;#analyze-miss&#34; class=&#34;header-anchor-link&#34;&gt;
&lt;svg
    xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;
    width=&#34;1rem&#34; height=&#34;1rem&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;
